'''Raynor Mining Enterprises''' was a prospecting and mining corporation that existed during the time of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]]. Founded by [[Trebold Raynor]], the company was somewhat notorious for their strategy of buying a [[Planet/Legends|planet]], harvesting all available resources, (whether they be [[Mineral/Legends|mineral]], [[Ore/Legends|ore]], or [[Crystal/Legends|crystal]]) and then abandoning it.

